These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Transport: jet-ski, airplane, snowmobile
1. Transport:airplane is on the right of Transport:snowmobile##1
2. Transport:jet-ski is on the far right##1
3. Transport:jet-ski is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | airplane | jet-ski |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
House: tower, wooden, ranch-style
1. House:wooden is in an odd position##4
2. House:tower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| House   | tower | ranch-style | wooden |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Birthday: october, june, august
1. Birthday:june is in an even position##4
2. Birthday:june is on the left or right of Birthday:august##3
3. Birthday:august is on the right of Birthday:june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Birthday   | october | june | august |

 #################################
 
